<div class="xar-mod-head">
    <span class="xar-mod-title"><xar:mlstring>Recommend Administration</xar:mlstring></span>
</div>
<div class="xar-mod-body">
    <img src="modules/adminpanels/xarimages/admin.gif" class="xar-module-icon" alt="official icon" width="96" height="96" />
    <h2><xar:mlstring>Overview</xar:mlstring></h2>

    <h3>
            <xar:mlstring>What is it?</xar:mlstring>
    </h3>
    <p>
        <xar:mlstring>
        The Recommend module allows visitors to your website a chance to send out
        recommendations to their friends. The module provides a form to allow visitors to
        recommend your site to others via email. In addition there is a custom 'send to friend'
        tag that you can use in your article templates allowing visitors to send a recommendation
         for a specific article.
         </xar:mlstring>
       </p>
    <h3>
            <xar:mlstring>How to use it?</xar:mlstring>
    </h3>
    <p>
        <xar:mlstring>From the menu, you have one choice. </xar:mlstring>
        <xar:mlstring>"Modify Configuration".  From this menu option, you can set the template
        that will be used for the email that is sent out, as well as override that choice and
        allow users to send their own message.</xar:mlstring>
        </p>
    <h3>
            <xar:mlstring>Included Blocks</xar:mlstring>
    </h3>
    <p>
            <xar:mlstring>There are no included blocks with this module.</xar:mlstring>
    </p>

    <h3>
            <xar:mlstring>Included Hooks</xar:mlstring>
    </h3>
    <p>
            <xar:mlstring>There are no included hooks with this module.</xar:mlstring>
    </p>

    <h3>
            <xar:mlstring>Included Custom Tags</xar:mlstring>
    </h3>
    <p>
        <xar:mlstring>There is a custom 'send to friend' tag included. The tag is placed in
        your article summary or display templates where you would like the 'send to a friend'
        icon or text to appear. The syntax is:</xar:mlstring>
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <code>
                &lt;xar:recommend-sendtofriend type="icon" /&gt;
            </code>
            <xar:mlstring>will add a small email icon in your template
            whereever the tag is placed. Clicking on the icon will display the Recommend email form with a link to the
            specific article.</xar:mlstring>
        </li>
        <li>
            <code>
                &lt;xar:recommend-sendtofriend type="text" /&gt;
            </code>
            <xar:mlstring>will add a 'send to friend' text
            link in your template whereever the tag is placed. Clicking on the link will display the Recommend email form with a link to the
            specific article.</xar:mlstring>
        </li>
     </ul>
      <p>
            <xar:mlstring>The email used in 'send to a friend' is customizable by overriding the user-usersendtofriend-text.xd and user-usersendtofriend-html.xd templates</xar:mlstring>
      </p>
      <h3>
            <xar:mlstring>Further Information</xar:mlstring>
      </h3>
